narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned how to use some software and imaging tools to 3D render objects.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Very disorganized and paced too slowly. Klaus had great pace but Alberto went too slowly and did not provide the information we needed to complete the assignments.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I assume this course will be much better next year. The teaching staff is great, so as long as they take all the feedback under consideration it should be worth taking next year.
